Resistance Breakout Research¶

Date 24 Feb 2020¶

Resistance Breakout - For High Volume/ High Liquidity instruments/ High Activity/ Fairly volatile/High Action

Breakout Rule¶

  • Price breached a assumed resistance level
  • A rolling maximum price is breached

  • A rolling maximum volume level is breached

  • 3 mins chart with 20 bars

Stop Loss¶

  • A previous price +/- 20 period ATR as trailing stop loss
